  fhir:DomainResource.text [
     fhir:Narrative.status [ fhir:value "extensions" ] ;
     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<div>\n    <table class=\"grid dict\">\n        \n        <tr>\n            <th scope=\"row\"><b>Id: </b></th>\n            <td style=\"padding-left: 4px;\">IMMZD2DTPolioSequentialIPVbOPV</td>\n        </tr>\n        \n\n        \n        <tr>\n            <th scope=\"row\"><b>Url: </b></th>\n            <td style=\"padding-left: 4px;\"><a href=\"PlanDefinition-IMMZD2DTPolioSequentialIPVbOPV.html\">IMMZ.D2.DT.Polio.Sequential IPV–bOPV</a></td>\n        </tr>\n        \n\n        \n        <tr>\n            <th scope=\"row\"><b>Version: </b></th>\n            <td style=\"padding-left: 4px;\">0.2.0</td>\n        </tr>\n        \n\n        \n\n        \n        <tr>\n            <th scope=\"row\"><b>Title: </b></th>\n            <td style=\"padding-left: 4px;\">IMMZ.D2.DT.Polio.Sequential IPV–bOPV</td>\n        </tr>\n        \n\n        \n\n        \n        <tr>\n            <th scope=\"row\"><b>Status: </b></th>\n            <td style=\"padding-left: 4px;\">draft</td>\n        </tr>\n        \n\n        \n\n        \n        <tr>\n            <th scope=\"row\"><b>Type: </b></th>\n            <td style=\"padding-left: 4px;\">\n                \n                    \n                        \n                        <p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">\n                            <b>system: </b> <span><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/7.2.0/CodeSystem-plan-definition-type.html\">http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/plan-definition-type</a></span>\n                        </p>\n                        \n                        \n                        <p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">\n                            <b>code: </b> <span>eca-rule</span>\n                        </p>\n                        \n                        \n                    \n                \n                \n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        \n\n        \n\n        \n        <tr>\n            <th scope=\"row\"><b>Date: </b></th>\n            <td style=\"padding-left: 4px;\">2026-07-20 11:34:37+0000</td>\n        </tr>\n        \n\n        \n        <tr>\n            <th scope=\"row\"><b>Publisher: </b></th>\n            <td style=\"padding-left: 4px;\">WHO</td>\n        </tr>\n        \n\n        \n        <tr>\n            <th scope=\"row\"><b>Description: </b></th>\n            <td style=\"padding-left: 4px;\"><div><p>IMMZ.D2.DT.Polio.Sequential IPV–bOPV\nSequential \"Bivalent oral polio vaccine (bOPV)–inactivated polio vaccine (IPV)\" schedule (in countries with high vaccination coverage [e.g. 90–95%] and low importation risk [where neighbouring countries and/or countries that share substantial population movement have a similarly high coverage])</p>\n</div></td>\n        </tr>\n        \n\n        \n        <tr>\n            <th scope=\"row\"><b>Knowledge Capability: </b></th>\n            <td style=\"padding-left: 4px;\">\n                \n                computable \n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        \n\n        \n\n        \n\n        \n\n        \n\n        \n\n        \n\n        \n\n        \n\n        \n\n        \n        <tr>\n            <th scope=\"row\"><b>Related Artifacts: </b></th>\n            <td style=\"padding-left: 4px;\">\n                \n                \n                <p><b>References</b></p>\n                <ul>\n                    \n                    <li><div><p>WHO recommendations for routine immunization - summary tables (January 2025)</p>\n</div><br/><a href=\"null\"/></li>\n                    \n                </ul>\n                \n                \n                \n                \n                \n                \n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        \n\n        \n        <tr>\n            <th scope=\"row\"><b>Libraries: </b></th>\n            <td style=\"padding-left: 4px;\">\n                <table class=\"grid-dict\">\n                    \n                    <tr>\n                        <td><a href=\"Library-IMMZD2DTPolioSequentialIPVbOPVLogic.html\">IMMZD2DTPolioSequentialIPVbOPVLogic</a></td>\n                    </tr>\n                    \n                </table>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        \n\n        \n        <tr>\n            <th scope=\"row\"><b>Actions: </b></th>\n            <td style=\"padding-left: 4px;\">\n                <table class=\"grid-dict\">\n                    \n                    <tr>\n                        <td>\n                            \n                            <b> Determine if the client is due for a poliovirus vaccination according to the national immunization schedule:</b> Determine if the client is due for a poliovirus vaccination according to the national immunization schedule\nSequential  \"Bivalent oral polio vaccine (bOPV)–inactivated polio vaccine (IPV)\" schedule (in countries with high \nvaccination coverage [e.g. 90–95%] and low importation risk [where neighbouring countries and/or countries that share \nsubstantial population movement have a similarly high coverage])\n                            \n                            <br/>\n                            \n                            \n                            <b>If:</b>\n                            \n                            <i>Applicability:</i>\n                            \n                            Client is due for IPV vaccination\n                            \n                            <i>(Client is due for IPV vaccination)</i>\n                            <br/>\n                            \n                            \n                            \n                            \n                            <b>Then:</b> <i>Definition:</i> <a href=\"ActivityDefinition-IMMZD2DTMR.html\">IMMZD2DTMR</a><br/>\n                            \n                            <i>Dynamic Values:</i><br/>\n                            \n                            status: <i>('draft')</i>\n                            <br/>\n                            \n                            intent: <i>('proposal')</i>\n                            <br/>\n                            \n                            medication: <i>(Concept { codes: { Code { system: 'http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.Z', code: 'DE31', display: 'Inactivated polio vaccines' } }, display: 'Inactivated polio vaccines' })</i>\n                            <br/>\n                            \n                            \n                            \n                            \n                        </td>\n                    </tr>\n                    \n                    <tr>\n                        <td>\n                            \n                            <b> Determine if the client is due for a poliovirus vaccination according to the national immunization schedule:</b> Determine if the client is due for a poliovirus vaccination according to the national immunization schedule\nSequential  \"Bivalent oral polio vaccine (bOPV)–inactivated polio vaccine (IPV)\" schedule (in countries with high \nvaccination coverage [e.g. 90–95%] and low importation risk [where neighbouring countries and/or countries that share \nsubstantial population movement have a similarly high coverage])\n                            \n                            <br/>\n                            \n                            \n                            <b>If:</b>\n                            \n                            <i>Applicability:</i>\n                            \n                            Client is due for bOPV vaccination\n                            \n                            <i>(Client is due for bOPV vaccination)</i>\n                            <br/>\n                            \n                            \n                            \n                            \n                            <b>Then:</b> <i>Definition:</i> <a href=\"ActivityDefinition-IMMZD2DTMR.html\">IMMZD2DTMR</a><br/>\n                            \n                            <i>Dynamic Values:</i><br/>\n                            \n                            status: <i>('draft')</i>\n                            <br/>\n                            \n                            intent: <i>('proposal')</i>\n                            <br/>\n                            \n                            medication: <i>(Concept { codes: { Code { system: 'http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.Z', code: 'DE30', display: 'Oral polio vaccines' } }, display: 'Oral polio vaccines' })</i>\n                            <br/>\n                            \n                            \n                            \n                            \n                        </td>\n                    </tr>\n                    \n                    <tr>\n                        <td>\n                            \n                            <b> Check for Guidance for the patient regarding IMMZ.D2.DT.Polio.Sequential IPV–bOPV.:</b> Show Guidance for the patient regarding IMMZ.D2.DT.Polio.Sequential IPV–bOPV.\n                            \n                            <br/>\n                            \n                            \n                            <b>If:</b>\n                            \n                            <i>Applicability:</i>\n                            \n                            Has Guidance\n                            \n                            <i>(Has Guidance)</i>\n                            <br/>\n                            \n                            \n                            \n                            \n                            <b>Then:</b> <i>Definition:</i> <a href=\"ActivityDefinition-IMMZD2DTCR.html\">IMMZ.D2.DT.CR</a><br/>\n                            \n                            <i>Dynamic Values:</i><br/>\n                            \n                            status: <i>('active')</i>\n                            <br/>\n                            \n                            payload.contentString: <i>(Guidance)</i>\n                            <br/>\n                            \n                            category.coding: <i>(Code { system: 'http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/communication-category', code: 'alert' })</i>\n                            <br/>\n                            \n                            priority: <i>(Code { system: 'http://hl7.org/fhir/request-priority', code: 'routine' })</i>\n                            <br/>\n                            \n                            \n                            \n                            \n                        </td>\n                    </tr>\n                    \n                </table>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        \n    </table>\n</div>\n</div>"
  ] ;
  fhir:DomainResource.contained [
     a fhir:Library ;
     fhir:index 0 ;
     fhir:Resource.id [ fhir:value "effective-data-requirements" ] ;
     fhir:DomainResource.extension [
       fhir:index 0 ;
       fhir:Element.extension [
         fhir:index 0 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "libraryName" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "IMMZElements" ]
       ], [
         fhir:index 1 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "name" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "Doses Administered to Patient" ]
       ], [
         fhir:index 2 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "statement" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "/**\n * @dataElement All Doses Administered to Patient\n */\ndefine \"Doses Administered to Patient\":\n  [Immunization] I\n    where I.status = 'completed'\n    and I.isSubpotent is not true" ]
       ], [
         fhir:index 3 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "displaySequence" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueInteger [ fhir:value "0"^^xsd:integer ]
       ] ;
       fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/cqf-logicDefinition" ]
     ], [
       fhir:index 1 ;
       fhir:Element.extension [
         fhir:index 0 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "libraryName" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "IMMZD2DTPolioElements" ]
       ], [
         fhir:index 1 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "name" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "Polio Doses Administered to Patient" ]
       ], [
         fhir:index 2 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "statement" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "/*\n@internal: Polio containing Doses Administered to Patient\n*/\ndefine \"Polio Doses Administered to Patient\":\n  Elements.\"Doses Administered to Patient\" I\n  where\n    I.vaccineCode in Concepts.\"Poliovirus-containing vaccines\"" ]
       ], [
         fhir:index 3 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "displaySequence" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueInteger [ fhir:value "1"^^xsd:integer ]
       ] ;
       fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/cqf-logicDefinition" ]
     ], [
       fhir:index 2 ;
       fhir:Element.extension [
         fhir:index 0 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "libraryName" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "IMMZD2DTPolioElements" ]
       ], [
         fhir:index 1 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "name" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "Polio Primary Series Doses Administered to Patient" ]
       ], [
         fhir:index 2 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "statement" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "/*\n@internal: Polio containing Doses Administered to Patient that are in the Primary series\n*/\ndefine \"Polio Primary Series Doses Administered to Patient\":\n  \"Polio Doses Administered to Patient\".seriesPrimary()" ]
       ], [
         fhir:index 3 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "displaySequence" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueInteger [ fhir:value "2"^^xsd:integer ]
       ] ;
       fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/cqf-logicDefinition" ]
     ], [
       fhir:index 3 ;
       fhir:Element.extension [
         fhir:index 0 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "libraryName" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "IMMZD2DTPolioEncounterElements" ]
       ], [
         fhir:index 1 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "name" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "Polio Primary Series Doses Administered to Patient" ]
       ], [
         fhir:index 2 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "statement" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "/*\n@internal: Polio containing Doses Administered to Patient that are in the Primary series\n*/\ndefine \"Polio Primary Series Doses Administered to Patient\":\n  PolioElements.\"Polio Primary Series Doses Administered to Patient\".onOrBefore(Today)" ]
       ], [
         fhir:index 3 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "displaySequence" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueInteger [ fhir:value "3"^^xsd:integer ]
       ] ;
       fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/cqf-logicDefinition" ]
     ], [
       fhir:index 4 ;
       fhir:Element.extension [
         fhir:index 0 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "libraryName" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "IMMZD2DTPolioEncounterElements" ]
       ], [
         fhir:index 1 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "name" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "Number of Polio Primary Series Doses Administered" ]
       ], [
         fhir:index 2 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "statement" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "/*\n@internal: Number of Polio Primary Series doses\n*/\ndefine \"Number of Polio Primary Series Doses Administered\":\n  Count(\"Polio Primary Series Doses Administered to Patient\")" ]
       ], [
         fhir:index 3 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "displaySequence" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueInteger [ fhir:value "4"^^xsd:integer ]
       ] ;
       fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/cqf-logicDefinition" ]
     ], [
       fhir:index 5 ;
       fhir:Element.extension [
         fhir:index 0 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "libraryName" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "IMMZD2DTPolioEncounterElements" ]
       ], [
         fhir:index 1 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "name" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "No poliovirus primary series doses were administered" ]
       ], [
         fhir:index 2 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "statement" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "/*\n@input: No poliovirus primary series doses were administered\n@pseudocode: Count of vaccines administered (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Poliovirus-containing vaccines\" and \"Type of dose\" = \"Primary series\") = 0\n@code: No poliovirus primary series doses were administered-130\n@decision: IMMZ.D2.DT.Polio.bOPV plus IPV: \"Bivalent oral polio vaccine (bOPV) plus inactivated polio vaccine (IPV)\" schedule (applicable for all countries)\n@decision: IMMZ.D2.DT.Polio.Sequential IPV–bOPV: Sequential \"Bivalent oral polio vaccine (bOPV)–inactivated polio vaccine (IPV)\" schedule (in countries with high vaccination coverage [e.g. 90–95%] and low importation risk [where neighbouring countries and/or countries that share substantial population movement have a similarly high coverage])\n@decision: IMMZ.D2.DT.Polio.IPV-only: Inactivated polio vaccine (IPV)-only (in countries, in polio-free regions, with a very low risk of importation and sustained high routine immunization coverage (third dose of the diphtheria–tetanus–pertussis vaccine [DTP3] > 90%)\n*/\ndefine \"No poliovirus primary series doses were administered\":\n  \"Number of Polio Primary Series Doses Administered\" = 0" ]
       ], [
         fhir:index 3 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "displaySequence" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueInteger [ fhir:value "5"^^xsd:integer ]
       ] ;
       fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/cqf-logicDefinition" ]
     ], [
       fhir:index 6 ;
       fhir:Element.extension [
         fhir:index 0 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "libraryName" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "IMMZEncounterElements" ]
       ], [
         fhir:index 1 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "name" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "Current Patient Age In Weeks" ]
       ], [
         fhir:index 2 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "statement" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "/** \n * @dataElement Patient age in weeks\n */\ndefine \"Current Patient Age In Weeks\":\n  AgeInWeeksAt(Today)" ]
       ], [
         fhir:index 3 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "displaySequence" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueInteger [ fhir:value "6"^^xsd:integer ]
       ] ;
       fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/cqf-logicDefinition" ]
     ], [
       fhir:index 7 ;
       fhir:Element.extension [
         fhir:index 0 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "libraryName" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "IMMZD2DTPolioEncounterElements" ]
       ], [
         fhir:index 1 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "name" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "Client's age is less than 8 weeks" ]
       ], [
         fhir:index 2 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "statement" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "/*\n@input: Client's age is less than 8 weeks\n@pseudocode: Today's date − \"Date of birth\" < 8 weeks\n@code: Client's age is less than 8 weeks-40\n@decision: IMMZ.D2.DT.Polio.Sequential IPV–bOPV: Sequential \"Bivalent oral polio vaccine (bOPV)–inactivated polio vaccine (IPV)\" schedule (in countries with high vaccination coverage [e.g. 90–95%] and low importation risk [where neighbouring countries and/or countries that share substantial population movement have a similarly high coverage])\n*/\ndefine \"Client's age is less than 8 weeks\":\n  Encounter.\"Current Patient Age In Weeks\" < 8" ]
       ], [
         fhir:index 3 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "displaySequence" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueInteger [ fhir:value "7"^^xsd:integer ]
       ] ;
       fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/cqf-logicDefinition" ]
     ], [
       fhir:index 8 ;
       fhir:Element.extension [
         fhir:index 0 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "libraryName" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "IMMZD2DTPolioSequentialIPVbOPVLogic" ]
       ], [
         fhir:index 1 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "name" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "Client is not due for IPV vaccination Case 1" ]
       ], [
         fhir:index 2 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "statement" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueString [ fhir:value "/*\n@output: Client is not due for IPV vaccination Case 1\n@pseudocode: \"Immunization recommendation status\" = \"Not due\"\n*/\ndefine \"Client is not due for IPV vaccination Case 1\":\n  Encounter.\"No poliovirus primary series doses were administered\"\n    and Encounter.\"Client's age is less than 8 weeks\"" ]
       ], [
         fhir:index 3 ;
         fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "displaySequence" ] ;
         fhir:Extension.valueInteger [ fhir:value "8"^^xsd:integer ]
       ] ;
       fhir:Extension.url [ fhir:value "http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/cqf-logicDefinition" ]
     ], [
       fhir:index 9 ;
